The manager has been a very complicated role in football since the sport grew popular, but it's never easy to explain what exact duties a manager shoulders in a team. Meanwhile, the evolution of football itself and different circumstances in the game further complicate what a manager means to their team. That's why finding a proper manager who can play the correct role matters a lot to a franchise. Host: Li Xiang Guest: Josh McNally Cover designer: Feng Yuan Chief editor: Chen Ran Supervisor: Zhang Shilei